 skills. Example Assistant Manager requirements Associate's degree required 2+ years' experience in upscale retail Excellent interpersonal skills Leadership Proficiency using CRM software Knowledge of up-selling Assistant Manager related job titles: Assistant Manager (Part-Time) Junior Supervisor Shift Manager Associate Manager Retail manager Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
